 />\n同一個身家千萬 遊手好閒二世祖<br />\n<br />\n啲女都係揀後者<br />\n千祈唔好搞錯"},{"pid":"3d24545ea112422c8be3477a3936d78c1f721b1a","tid":496402,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>太宰治點解可以溝咁多女 係咪果陣d女唔睇有冇上進心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上進心=有錢<br />\n<br />\n一個朝九晚六 勤奮打工仔<br />\n同一個身家千萬 遊手好閒二世祖<br />\n<br />\n啲女都係揀後者<br />\n千祈唔好搞錯</blockquote><br />\n太宰治就算屋企有錢佢個幾條女都唔撚知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b61714060b00e57817554e7e58c18ec060e4fba","tid":496402,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"點解D人話佢係太善良呢<br />\n我見到佢係成日將人地好意解讀做有目的, 中性既野解做惡意喎"},{"pid":"db3cc2497536e38761412fc7fb8ba7d90ce1e63b","tid":496402,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d3ed391c38898d2d36dd32bb6de0f8cdfd46919","tid":496402,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c52d6fd382e231e005f7e7f597d09f57daa05ec8","tid":496402,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}